OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FA blockade of Dublin's main
OL,8,Fthoroughfare has been cleared in a
OL,9,Flate-night police operation, ahead of
OL,10,Fan emergency Cabinet meeting to sign
OL,11,Foff on measures the Irish Government
OL,12,Fhopes will bring all protests over
OL,13,Ffuel costs to an end.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
