PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FThe protests ` which involved
OL,8,Fblockades of streets in the capital,
OL,9,FIreland's only oil refinery, and key
OL,10,Fdepots ` strangled fuel distribution
OL,11,Facross the country and prompted an
OL,12,Fescalated policing response that
OL,13,Fresulted in several arrests and public
OL,14,Forder gardai deployed in Cork, Galway
OL,15,Fand Dublin.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FParticipants ` largely led by
OL,8,Fhauliers, farmers, and agricultural
OL,9,Fworkers ` began separate but co-
OL,10,Fordinated action on Tuesday with slow-
OL,11,Fmoving convoys and outright stoppages
OL,12,Fon major motorways, as well as
OL,13,Fblockades of critical infrastructure.
OL,15,FSome protests rolled overnight into
OL,16,FSunday morning, with spokesmen calling
OL,17,Fon the Government to take urgent
OL,18,Faction to reduce fuel costs which they
OL,19,Fsay are at unsustainable levels and
OL,20,Fwill lead to people going out of
OL,21,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FThe coalition Government is expected
OL,8,Fto sign off on fuel-cost measures on
OL,9,FSunday evening, but it remains to be
OL,10,Fseen if it will convince protesters to
OL,11,Fcall off their actions before the
OL,12,Freturn of schools on Monday adds to
OL,13,Fpressure on the roads.
OL,15,FThe Irish police service, An Garda
OL,16,FSiochana, cleared a blockade of the
OL,17,FWhitegate oil refinery in Co Cork
OL,18,Faround lunchtime on Saturday and vowed
OL,19,Fto implement further enhanced
OL,20,Fenforcement actions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FIt saw physical clashes between
OL,8,Fprotesters and gardai, who used pepper
OL,9,Fspray during the hour-long operation
OL,10,Fwhich resecured access for fuel trucks.
OL,12,FGardai were later called to a similar
OL,13,Faction at Galway harbour, where
OL,14,Fhundreds of protesters gathered in
OL,15,Fpouring rain while restricting access
OL,16,Fto a fuel depot by blocking the way
OL,17,Fwith tractors.
OL,19,FMembers of the Public Order Unit,
OL,20,Fwearing protective gear and batons,
OL,21,Fwere at the scene for hours overnight.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FOn Sunday morning, An Garda Siochana
OL,8,Fannounced all blockades in Dublin had
OL,9,Fbeen cleared following an overnight
OL,10,Foperation on O'Connell Street.
OL,12,FIt said illegally parked vehicles
OL,13,Fwould be removed and blockading
OL,14,Fvehicles were removed under escort.
OL,16,FGarda Commissioner Justin Kelly had
OL,17,Fvowed to step up enforcement against
OL,18,Ffuel-cost protesters "endangering the
OL,19,Fstate" by blocking critical
OL,20,Finfrastructure.
OL,26,@zD@VOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FProtesters' demands for meetings with
OL,8,FGovernment were not acceded to but
OL,9,Frelevant ministers held talks with
OL,10,Festablished national representative
OL,11,Fbodies on Friday and Saturday.
OL,13,FThese meetings concluded with a
OL,14,F"substantial" package involving a
OL,15,Ftemporary fuel transport support
OL,16,Fscheme" and "temporary fuel support".
OL,18,FIt is understood the transport support
OL,19,Fscheme will see direct payments to
OL,20,Fbusinesses in the sectors affected by
OL,21,Fhigh fuel costs.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]xD@GO]xD@MOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FA senior source said the scheme will
OL,8,Fbe part of a broader package on the
OL,9,Ffuel crisis.
OL,11,FThe engagements included Irish Road
OL,12,FHaulage Association president Ger
OL,13,FHyland, who said there were "the bones
OL,14,Fof an agreement" with the Government.
OL,16,FHe added he hoped the "substantial
OL,17,Fpackage", understood to include a
OL,18,Fdirect payment scheme, would be agreed
OL,19,Fby Sunday morning.
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@PO]xD@WOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FThe Cabinet is due to meet on Sunday
OL,8,Fafternoon to sign off on the measures.
OL,10,FThe pledge of a "substantial" package
OL,11,Fwas not enough to dissuade protesters
OL,12,Faway from their blockades without
OL,13,FGarda intervention on Saturday.
OL,15,FCommissioner Kelly said: "Some people
OL,16,Fhave decided to escalate an already
OL,17,Fdifficult situation by blockading
OL,18,Fcritical national infrastructure such
OL,19,Fas fuel depots and refineries.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@]O]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,F"This has resulted in fuel shortages
OL,8,Fthat are directly impacting on
OL,9,Femergency services such as hospitals,
OL,10,Fthe ambulance service and the fire
OL,11,Fservice, as well as businesses and the
OL,12,Fgeneral public.
OL,14,F"These are blockades. They are not a
OL,15,Flegitimate form of protest."
OL,17,FHe said: "We gave the blockaders fair
OL,18,Fwarning that we were moving to
OL,19,Fenforcement and they choose to ignore
OL,20,Fit and continue to hold the country to
OL,21,Fransom."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@\O]yD@JOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
