CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FA small number of Defence Forces
OL,8,Fpersonnel with heavy-lift recovery
OL,9,Ftrucks have been on standby to assist
OL,10,Fgardai with moving large vehicles if
OL,11,Fneeded.
OL,13,FThe escalated enforcement action came
OL,14,Fafter Fuels for Ireland chief
OL,15,Fexecutive Kevin McPartlan said around
OL,16,F600 of the 1,500 filling stations in
OL,17,Fthe Republic of Ireland had run dry on
OL,18,FSaturday morning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
