PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776041695
OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FHe predicted the number "would grow
OL,8,Fquite dramatically" if the blockades
OL,9,Fon Whitegate in Galway and Foynes, Co
OL,10,FLimerick, continued.
OL,12,FBlockades have resulted in full
OL,13,Fclosures of parts of the M50 ring road
OL,14,Faround Dublin, as well as other major
OL,15,Fmotorways, although Gardai announced
OL,16,Fblockades on the M50 at junctions five
OL,17,Fand seven had been cleared on Sunday
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
