OL,3,CFuel protest 'cleared' from Dublin as
OL,4,CCabinet prepares to hold emergency
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FMeanwhile, police in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fsaid they are "maintaining an ongoing
OL,9,Fassessment" in relation to social
OL,10,Fmedia posts calling for similar
OL,11,Fplanned protests there.
OL,13,FA PSNI spokeswoman said: "A policing
OL,14,Fresponse has been prepared, if needed,
OL,15,Fto ensure public safety and to help
OL,16,Fminimise any potential disruption to
OL,17,Fthe wider community."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
